2018年11月22日，[[三星電子|三星電子]]在三星開發者大會中宣布以[[One_UI|One UI]]取代目前Samsung Experience使用者界面<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mobilityarena.com/samsung-one-ui-the-experience-ui-replacement/|title=This is Samsung One UI, the Experience UI replacement|accessdate=2018-12-05T03:14:31Z|date=2018-11-08|last=Mobility|first=Mister|work=MobilityArena|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181205103624/https://mobilityarena.com/samsung-one-ui-the-experience-ui-replacement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全新的[[使用者界面|使用者界面]]包括黑夜模式等多項新功能。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.samsung.com/global/galaxy/apps/one-ui/|title=One UI {{!}} Apps|accessdate=2018-12-05T03:15:16Z|work=The Official Samsung Galaxy Site|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130072721/https://www.samsung.com/global/galaxy/apps/one-ui/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

